Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: This new building (built late 2019) is located in one of the fastest growing commercial nodes in the Oromocto Area. Located adjacent to the highway and seconds away from the turn off, this location lends itself well to fast food (previous use), retail, and other businesses looking for a prime location
Multiple retail units available, ranging in size and rent. See the flyer for more details!

Plaza West is the newest commercial Development in Oromocto West. This is a Multi Tenant complex currently plan to accommodate ~ 16,000 SF of retail space accommodating suites from ~1,000 and up. Suite can be combined. Key design elements are focused on community convenience, easy access for customers, including drive-thru options for some end cap suites. Large display windows and signage options are also available. See the flyer for more details!
Multiple units ranging in size that can be combined, see the flyer for more details!
